          about

          A piece born out of improvisation between Matthew Hayes and Aarti Jadu.

          artwork by Helen Gory

          lyrics

          words:-
          I thought that you were just eyes
          that took too long to stray
          and that the details of your face accidentally fell in place
          to find mine
          and pause time
          are you so decent to not be curious

          by Aarti Jadu

          credits

          released April 6, 2019
          vocals: Aarti Jadu
          electric solo bass: Matthew Hayes
          intro vocals: Lizzie Bruk
          synth pads: Matthew Hayes
          violin: Aurora Darby
          other instrumentation: Aarti Jadu

          strings recorded by Ariel Blum

          mixed + produced by Aarti Jadu
          special thanks to Kane Anthony with mixing

          mastered by Joe Talia
